# Josep Bernad

> Josep Bernad is a house music DJ, multi-instrumentalist, and software engineer from Mallorca, Spain, based in Barcelona. He produces original house music and performs three live formats: a Live Set with live instruments, a House DJ Set, and a Party Set (Open Format) for festivals and private events.

This site is the official home for Josep Bernad's music: original productions, live and DJ set films, upcoming shows, booking information, and press materials. The site is published in English, Spanish, and Catalan; the structured data and meta on every page are intentionally LLM-friendly.

